{"tid":1593213,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[分析] 9月開始，港共 對 香港人 既最新策略","createTime":"2019-09-25T03:35:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T08:29:22.000Z","uid":158613,"like":30,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"d742acfad6735df6fc9dd5f30b64336895ebf174","tid":1593213,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:35:19.000Z","msg":"最近對家出緊兩招<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>1: 引到大家去查案，但同時，製造大量假新聞<br />\n (我信831有死人，只是苦無証據)</strong><br />\n<strong>2: 引到大家將武力升級，但同時，黑警就馬上喬裝，四出破壞同放火<br />\n以上兩招，都係用媒體配合，馬上盡力唱衰抹黑</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n老毛格言：凡是敵人反對的，我們就要擁護；<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">凡是敵人擁護的，我們就要反對。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>敵人開始擁護緊我地既查案同勇武</ins></strong>，大家係時候要小心考慮如何處理<br />\n<br />\n理解大家都好緊張手足<br />\n但真係要FC，要有思考，唔好比人帶風向，要返回正軌"},{"pid":"ed69ea681a33d9d4242e2ef0ef47e215709e2578","tid":1593213,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好撚癲，香港冇大台運動，已經發展到929全球冇大台反支運動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1592119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1592119</a>"},{"pid":"5d032e7f0aa66276e72feb77c0af560692c24aee","tid":1593213,"uid":274161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:39:24.000Z","msg":"引導大家將武力升級：<br />\n上兩個星期用藍絲同黑社會（所謂愛國人士），<br />\n尋日直接上黑警打議員、記者、法輪功（注意法輪功被襲人士當時去差舘討論十一遊行事宜），<br />\n呢兩個星期拘捕十幾嵗細路都幾多<br />\n<br />\n總之就係挑動仇恨"},{"pid":"1d712fd6fd17c85099c1e430ecea79964d05a9b6","tid":1593213,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:42:55.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8894375515ad1b21b7c151f24cb5cdaabf18ad90","tid":1593213,"uid":202895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T03:43:58.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"4fce0f1d36a8c9