b2ddd282fe2b1b8c","tid":1593213,"uid":193215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-26T09:36:27.000Z","msg":"根本查案就同捉鬼一樣，搵到又如何，搞得掂條主線，呢啲支線想攻破又有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就算查案都唔使開咁多個post，仲要個個post都上到熱門，反而真正幫到成個抗爭運動嘅文宣同行動post就十個頂盡得三四個上到熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9b9d071826b74ef6228a16fd36ee19695a99080","tid":1593213,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T01:17:40.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"83126733a7086942b86e7eaf0ae4a5fe1ebdc8b2","tid":1593213,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:37:14.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"dc82965867b7d6174cffcdae41f5cea597847372","tid":1593213,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T02:37:52.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=ZBayvnjX3omFcj6xyood9JR%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=5d318b87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KzWre74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKzWre74.jpg&h=4920057f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OYiUo1r.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOYiUo1r.jpg&h=874df038&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wui5vGr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwui5vGr.jpg&h=3ed0def1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kBpHxUN.jpg\" 